><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg" width="662" height="478.2035175879397" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:575,&quot;width&quot;:796,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:662,&quot;bytes&quot;:58050,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb704563b-86e0-4bd6-bf3a-9c0b6c0163ad_796x575.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.sustainabilitybynumbers.com/p/renewables-waste">汉娜·里奇</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这里的关键事实是，煤炭产生的废物比太阳能或风能（或核能）多得多，但我们已经学会忽视煤炭废物及其造成的健康问题。太阳能将产生更少的废物。</p><p>这些废物的毒性也不会特别大。许多太阳能怀疑论者写信给我说太阳能电池板含有各种有害化学物质，但里奇指出，我们已经改用不含大多数这些化学物质的电池板技术：</p><blockquote><p>美国州卫生部门列出了太阳能电池板中的一系列潜在毒素：砷、镓、锗和六价铬。</p><p>除此之外，大多数面板都是晶体硅或碲化镉 (CdTe)，其中不含砷、镓、锗或六价铬。有关其中一些说法可能来自何处的更多信息，请参见脚注。 <a href="https://www.sustainabilitybynumbers.com/p/renewables-waste#footnote-5-138994586"><sup>5</sup></a></p><p>太阳能电池板唯一的健康问题是硅电池板中含有少量的铅，而 CdTe 电池板中含有微量的镉。国际能源署也将这些列为唯一潜在的人类健康风险。</p></blockquote><p>事实上，工程师们也在努力去除太阳能电池板上的少量铅。</p><p>太阳能怀疑论者是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/dont-be-a-decel">根深蒂固的技术悲观主义者</a>，并且始终低估人类围绕早期技术障碍进行创新的能力。</p><p>不过，我要指出的是，里奇并没有将太阳能与天然气进行比较，后者可能产生相对少量的固体或液体废物。这是一个重要且必要的比较。但仅仅表明太阳能产生的废物比美国人几十年来生活的煤电少得多，就表明太阳能废物问题不会成为问题。</p><h4> 5.不平等战争愈演愈烈</h4><p>早在 2010 年代，人们就对不平等加剧表示强烈抗议。托马斯·皮凯蒂（Thomas Piketty）、伊曼纽尔·赛斯（Emmanuel Saez）和加布里埃尔·祖克曼（Gabriel Zucman）等经济学家因传达的信息而声名鹊起，即不平等现象正在无情地加剧，需要通过极高的税收来遏制。但总有一些经济学家声称，美国不平等的加剧没有皮凯蒂等人那么剧烈。声称。</p><p>最引人注目的分歧通常是关于财富不平等，而财富不平等本质上是难以衡量的。但也存在关于收入不平等的争论。以下是<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2019-12-27/inequality-is-up-a-lot-the-question-is-how-much?sref=R8NfLgwS">我 2019 年为彭博社撰写的</a>文章：</p><blockquote><p>收入不平等也很难衡量……很多收入是公司在纸面上赚取的，而问题是其中有多少实际上属于这些公司的所有者……另一个问题是税收和转移支付如何改变收入。政府的一美元医疗保健支出是否应该算作受益者的一美元收入？</p><p>对此类问题的不同答案可能会产生截然不同的收入集中情况。皮凯蒂和赛斯估计，2012 年，最富有的 0.1% 人群的收入占国民收入的 12%；美联储和布鲁金斯学会团队<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/bpea-articles/measuring-income-and-wealth-at-the-top-using-administrative-and-survey-data/">得出的</a>数字都接近 8%，仅比 20 世纪 80 年代末稍高一点。与此同时，皮凯蒂、萨伊兹和祖克曼在<a href="http://gabriel-zucman.eu/files/PSZ2018QJE.pdf">2018 年发表的一篇论文</a>发现，即使考虑了税收和转移支付，最富有的 1% 人占据国民收入的比例也从 20 世纪 80 年代末的 10% 左右增至 2010 年代中期的 15% 以上。但 Gerald Auten 和 David Splinter 的<a href="http://davidsplinter.com/AutenSplinter-Tax_Data_and_Inequality.pdf">一篇论文</a>发现这个数字分别接近 7% 和 9%。国会预算办公室的分析得出的数字<a href="https://www.economist.com/briefing/2019/11/28/economists-are-rethinking-the-numbers-on-inequality">介于两者之间</a>，但更接近法国三国的数字。</p></blockquote><p>无论如何，这种分歧并没有消失。事实上，它只会变得更有活力。 Auten 和 Splinter 发表了<a href="https://www.davidsplinter.com/AutenSplinter-Tax_Data_and_Inequality.pdf">一篇新论文</a>，其中添加了更多调整，发现前 1% 的比例与 1960 年代相比<em>根本没有增加</em>！这是他们的图表，将他们自己的数据与皮凯蒂、赛斯和祖克曼的数据进行了比较： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg" width="932" height="365" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:365,&quot;width&quot;:932,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:75318,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3affa5c7-5f58-497d-ad1e-3829aee41c18_932x365.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这两个经济学家团队如何得到如此巨大不同的数字，尤其是当他们获得相同的数据时？两者之间的一些分歧是由于对数据本身的分歧，特别是关于处于分配底部的人们遗漏了多少收入的纳税申报表。奥滕和斯普林特认为这比皮凯蒂等人要多得多。思考。但很多分歧也只是由于对什么算作“收入”、什么不算作不同的选择造成的。</p><p>例如，一美元的健康福利算作一美元的收入吗？也许人们实际上并不以与现金一比一的比例来衡量健康福利。我知道，如果我的雇主决定将价值 500,000 美元的布丁送到我家来支付我的工资，我不会认为这与获得 500,000 美元的报酬是一样的。但也许健康福利和现金<em>一样有价值</em>？很难知道。</p><p>还有<em>估算租金</em>的问题。如果您拥有自己的房屋，您的住房费用会比租房者低。您每月因无需支付租金而节省的收入称为“估算租金”。但应该算作收入吗？一方面，你的口袋里确实有更多现金。另一方面，如果您不拥有自己的房屋，则不清楚您需要支付<em>多少</em>租金。</p><p>第三个问题涉及企业留存收益。假设我拥有一家赚取一定利润的公司，并且我想取出该利润。但由于股息和资本利得税非常高，我让公司保留这些钱并为我投资，而不是提取，我等待税率下降，这样我就可以把钱取出来花。这笔钱算不算我的收入？</p><p>类似这样的问题还有很多。你读皮凯蒂等人的论文以及奥滕和斯普林特的论文越多，你就越会意识到前者总是选择使不平等<em>最大化的</em>解释，而后者总是选择使不平等<em>最小化</em>的解释。团队似乎非常致力于他们的叙述；<a href="https://twitter.com/PikettyWIL/status/1727338489656803631">皮凯蒂在推特上怒吼道</a>，“否认不平等与否认气候变化一样危险。” （注：不，不是。）</p><p>似乎一个合理的结论是，事实——就单一客观“事实”存在的程度而言——位于中间的某个地方。奥滕和斯普林特的一些选择似乎合理，而另一些则似乎不太合理——估算租金显然是收入的一种形式，但收入不平等从 1980 年左右到 2010 年有所上升，但可能比皮凯蒂和他的合著者想象的要少。这是一个问题，但问题并不像最响亮的声音让我们相信的那么严重。这是2010年代其他研究收入不平等问题的研究团队得出的普遍结论，我认为这是最合理的。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-things-for-your-thanksgiving?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-things-for-your-thanksgiving?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>;
Feeling strangely optimistic about EgyptIt has many of the building blocks for a successful industrialization story. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/feeling-strangely-optimistic-about https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/feeling-strangely-optimistic-aboutNoah Smith Fri, 24 Nov 2023 08:25:01 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg" width="716" height="477.5643756050339" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:689,&quot;width&quot;:1033,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:716,&quot;bytes&quot;:341923,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2cf3a335-9ad2-4298-b6cc-944e444408d9_1033x689.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> “<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=95345269">中央商务区，埃及新的行政首都</a>”作者：Youssef Abdelwahab， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/?ref=openverse">CC BY 4.0</a> 。</figcaption></figure></div><p>意见作者从出租车司机那里获取话题想法是一种传统。几周前，当我前往机场前往爱尔兰和新加坡时，我的出租车司机（刚从埃及移民）要求我写一篇关于他的祖国的文章。</p><p>如果美国人真正考虑埃及的经济（他们通常不会这样做），他们通常会认为埃及经济一文不值。并且有一定的理由。它是一个主要是沙漠的中东国家，人口众多且不断增长，但<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_proven_oil_reserves">石油匮乏</a>，而且存在巨额贸易逆差。十年前，它因一场革命和随后的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2013_Egyptian_coup_d%27%C3%A9tat">军事政变</a>而动摇。这场政变的带头人阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西仍然掌管着这个国家。所有这些因素通常都会导致悲观的前景。</p><p>但当我有机会时，我仔细观察了埃及的经济状况，发现了一些值得鼓励的事情。首先，是整体增长轨迹。许多贫穷国家的国内生产总值都会经历一段时期的下降——它们变得更富或更穷，这取决于资源价格和国内政治局势。但埃及的 GDP 仅在 2011-14 年的混乱时期才趋于稳定；总体而言，它一直处于缓慢但稳定的上升轨道。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg" width="662" height="468.59215686274507" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:722,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:662,&quot;bytes&quot;:75940,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F91f62a07-830d-4e1b-90df-662f551e9399_1020x722.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>另请注意，尽管埃及的生活水平低于世界平均水平，但实际上并没有那么穷——与南非或印度尼西亚的水平大致相同。换句话说，它是一个坚实的中等收入国家。</p><p> （顺便说一句，一些美国人似乎没有意识到这一点，但许多发展中国家现在看起来是这样的——不再是一群生活在农村、自己种植食物的赤贫人口，而是一群有点——住在人口稠密的大城市的公寓楼里并从事当地服务行业的穷人。）</p><p>埃及的中等收入地位令人鼓舞的是，它不是基于出口。事实上，埃及根本不向外界出售那么多东西。其出口仅占GDP的15%， <a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NE.EXP.GNFS.ZS?locations=EG&amp;most_recent_value_desc=true">与大多数国家相比相当低</a>。它<a href="https://oec.world/en/profile/country/egy">最大的出口实际上是石油</a>，但它在境外销售的石油<em>总量</em>相当低——<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_oil_exports">大约只相当于人口相似的越南</a>。不管怎么想，埃及绝对不是一个石油国家。</p><p>因此，埃及的收入必须来自国内经济——来自埃及人互相制造商品和提供服务。该国几乎完全依靠其国内经济实现了中等收入地位，这一事实是一个令人鼓舞的迹象——这意味着基本经济机制正在以合理的效率发挥作用。将埃及与尼日利亚或巴基斯坦等真正的困境进行比较： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg" width="678" height="485.9" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:731,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:678,&quot;bytes&quot;:88846,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F190cfb5b-f452-49e3-8b57-b1fe49304c2b_1020x731.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这意味着，如果埃及确实开始增加出口，其增长将建立在相当高的现有基础之上。由于埃及的国内经济已证明其相对高效，因此出口增加的“乘数效应”可能会很大。所以就其在全球经济中的地位而言，埃及确实除了上升无路可走。</p><p>那么埃及成为出口国的前景如何？在研究了最近的各种<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-developing-country-industrialization">工业化成功案例</a>之后，我认为埃及应该尝试吸引<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-polandmalaysia-model">外国对制造业的直接投资</a>。近年来，埃及的大部分外国直接投资都进入了石油和天然气行业，很少进入制造业或可出口服务业： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg" width="656" height="312.30979498861046" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:418,&quot;width&quot;:878,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:656,&quot;bytes&quot;:109157,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6fcf1457-2c3f-49b1-b363-41368740e420_878x418.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.oecd.org/investment/OECD-Review-of-Foreign-Direct-Investment-Statistics-Egypt.pdf">经合组织</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>埃及确实拥有一些关键优势，使其成为出口导向型外国直接投资的潜在良好地点。首先是<strong>地理</strong>；埃及靠近欧洲，有很多海岸线，大部分人口都在海岸附近。因此，无论埃及生产什么出口商品，都可以非常快速且廉价地运往欧洲。</p><p>第二个优势是<strong>国内市场</strong>的潜力。埃及有1.13亿人口；再加上中等收入水平，你就有了相当大的潜在市场。在埃及建厂和设立分支机构的公司将更容易吸引这些消费者。这甚至没有考虑到中东和北非其他地区的市场，埃及可以作为当地的生产基地。</p><p>第三个优势是<strong>稳定性</strong>。在革命和政变刚刚过去十年后，我提出这样的说法似乎有些奇怪。但请注意，埃及与许多在阿拉伯之春期间经历动乱的周边国家不同，尽管埃及的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting-older">年轻人数量</a>有所增加，<em>但并未陷入内战</em>。该国没有重大的种族或民族分歧，只有与政治无关的次要宗教分歧（该国 13% 的人信奉基督教）。也不存在区域断层线；该国几乎每个人都居住在尼罗河沿岸或尼罗河三角洲。换句话说，不存在可以使埃及分裂的自然断层线。它是世界上最同质、最统一的人口之一。政府的主要意识形态反对派是穆斯林兄弟会，但到目前为止，他们并没有表现出成为武装叛乱分子的意愿。</p><p>第四个因素是<strong>阳光</strong>。埃及全年都有充足的阳光，并且有大量空置的沙漠土地来建设太阳能。在超廉价太阳能时代，埃及实际上拥有无限的电力资源。廉价、可靠的电力是制造业的关键投入。</p><p>最后，埃及在<strong>基础设施</strong>上投入了大量资金， <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/egypts-president-sisi-touts-megaprojects-ahead-of-march-vote-1518431400">特别是在塞西领导下</a>。最壮观、最引人注目的投资是开罗郊外的<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2022/10/08/world/middleeast/egypt-new-administrative-capital.html">新行政首都</a>，里面有摩天大楼、宫殿，甚至还有<a href="https://www.dezeen.com/2015/03/02/pyramid-inspired-skyscraper-zayed-crystal-spark-cairo-egypt/">玻璃金字塔</a>。 （有人可能会说，经济价值值得怀疑的大型华而不实的建设项目是埃及的传统。）但<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/egypts-president-sisi-touts-megaprojects-ahead-of-march-vote-1518431400">除了</a>华而不实的新首都之外，塞西还投资了一些基础设施，可以让外国公司的日子过得更轻松。这包括：</p><ul><li><p>一堆<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/egypts-road-building-drive-eases-jams-leaves-some-unhappy-2021-05-14/">新道路</a></p></li><li><p>一堆<a href="https://www.arabnews.com/node/2383741/middle-east">新住房</a></p></li><li><p>大型核电站</p></li><li><p>沙漠土地开垦</p></li><li><p>苏伊士运河拓宽</p></li></ul><p>我的出租车司机提到，这种基础设施建设实际上是埃及的主要积极因素。尽管塞西政府中的人们显然也<a href="https://www.egypttoday.com/Article/3/120282/Egypt-spends-400B-on-infrastructure-to-lure-investments">至少</a>在考虑吸引海外投资，但他可能更看重其对就业的影响，而不是吸引外国直接投资的有用性。所选择的投资不一定完全符合外国投资者的需求，但它们会有所帮助，最重要的是，它们表现出支出意愿和快速建设项目的管理能力。</p><p>因此，埃及拥有许多固有的优势，可以利用这些优势促进外国直接投资的繁荣。它也有一些固有的弱点。</p><p>最大的弱点是<strong>水资源供应</strong>。埃及实际上是地球上最干旱的国家；据<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/ER.H2O.INTR.PC?most_recent_value_desc=true">世界银行测算</a>，埃及人均可再生内陆淡水资源拥有量仅为9立方米，位居世界第三低，仅次于巴林和科威特。这是一个图表，仅供说明之用： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_1020x720.jpeg" width="630" height="444.70588235294116" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7075cc6c-8fdf-490c-a8a1-efe3948a1509_10