ackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg" width="658" height="493.5" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:960,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:658,&quot;bytes&quot;:270922,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6252af70-3b27-444f-88d0-107564cddaf5_960x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：美国宇航局</figcaption></figure></div><p>这个国家非常干燥，除了这条细细的河流沿岸之外，基本上不可能在任何地方居住。地球上没有其他国家的人口分布与埃及相似： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg" width="1338" height="795" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:795,&quot;width&quot;:1338,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:247738,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff66e7820-a400-4f34-b5d5-cb25516aec3b_1338x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：农业部</figcaption></figure></div><p>许多类型的制造业都非常耗水。对于这些人来说，埃及唯一真正的希望是利用海水淡化——海水淡化的成本正在<a href="https://www.warpnews.org/green-tech/desalination-of-salt-water-is-getting-cheaper-and-cheaper/">迅速降低</a>——并将工厂建在海岸上。廉价的太阳能会有所帮助。</p><p>但某些类型的制造业并不需要大量的水，制造业（包括建筑业）约占<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NV.IND.MANF.ZS">埃及 GDP 的 16%</a>就证明了这一点——就国家而言，这个比例相当高。因此，缺乏水资源并不一定是一个问题。</p><p>第二个障碍是<strong>教育水平</strong>低。以现代标准衡量，埃及的识字率相当低，约为 75%： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:131508,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59992d26-a7b4-4a45-aed4-14adb5a30190_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>制造商需要能读写的工人。一开始这不是问题，因为埃及有很多识字<em>的</em>人，而且中学入学率实际上<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/SE.SEC.ENRR?locations=EG">相当不错</a>。但从长远来看，任何外国直接投资的推动都需要更多的教育支出。</p><p>第三个问题是<strong>腐败</strong>，我的出租车司机对此深感不满。埃及在腐败措施方面得分很低，尽管它远不是最差的国家之一。关键问题是<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/egypts-military-is-under-pressure-to-loosen-its-grip-on-economy-b77d935d">军方拥有或控制着</a>该国的许多企业。这类似于20世纪末的印度尼西亚军队，或者今天的伊朗革命卫队。对商业的军事控制排挤了私营部门，而且由于缺乏竞争而常常效率低下。</p><p>尽管解决这个问题是一项长期挑战，但它并不一定会阻碍外国直接投资或制造业的增长。外资公司将不再拥有军事所有权，而在埃及于<a href="https://www.oecd-ilibrary.org/sites/8a873381-en/index.html?itemId=/content/component/8a873381-en">2017 年开始建立的</a>经济特区，外国公司将被课以轻税。这将使外国直接投资免受军事竞争和榨取的影响。军方不太可能太介意。他们将仅仅从流入埃及经济其他部分的收入中获得巨大的推动，使他们已经拥有的面向国内的企业受益。</p><p>印度尼西亚的军事独裁者苏哈托（其政治生涯与塞西的政治生涯有些相似）就是这样在上世纪 80 年代和 90 年代推动基于外国直接投资的制造业繁荣，尽管他的军队仍然控制着其他大部分经济领域。塞西应该有意识地效仿苏哈托的经济战略。</p><p>但埃及目前面临的最大危险不是腐败、文盲或缺水，而是外债。埃及的国内储蓄率非常低——仅占<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GNS.ICTR.ZS?most_recent_value_desc=true">GDP 的 13%</a> ——因此它无法真正为其一直以来的所有基础设施支出提供资金。相反，它大部分<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypt-faces-external-debt-reckoning-after-borrowing-spree-2023-06-06/">资金都是从国外借来的</a>。但埃及不能借到埃及镑；它必须借入美元、欧元或其他外币。</p><p>这使埃及处于巨大危险之中。请记住<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-sri-lanka-is-having-an-economic">典型的新兴市场危机</a>是如何运作的——一个国家借入大量外币计价的债务，然后其货币贬值，导致其无法偿还债务。然后，它要么违约，要么印钞，并承受恶性通货膨胀，这两者都会使经济陷入混乱（尽管恶性通货膨胀更糟）。埃及尤其面临此类危机的危险，因为它持续存在贸易逆差。这是<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/egypt-faces-external-debt-reckoning-after-borrowing-spree-2023-06-06/">路透社的报道</a>：</p><blockquote><p> [埃及政府]的大型项目很少能产生额外的硬通货流入……全球借贷成本攀升……在外汇紧缩的情况下，埃及在两年内从银行系统中提取了超过 400 亿美元的外国净资产，其中部分已使用支撑英镑……硬通货紧缩引发了人们对埃及偿还外债能力的<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/north-africa-backslides-toward-swirling-debt-troubles-2023-05-11/">担忧</a>。自四月份以来，三大主要信贷机构均下调了埃及债务前景…… </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71df-b8c2-419f-a967-ff57bff3ef65_891x585.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8f5c71